<font color=#FFFF00>Cut.</font>

988
00:49:28,856 --> 00:49:30,556
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang.</font>

989
00:49:34,316 --> 00:49:37,956
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka tidak lupa berpose untuk para penonton.</font>

990
00:49:38,656 --> 00:49:40,856
