00:50:39,056 --> 00:50:40,316
<font color=#FFFF00>"Dia menemukan kamera"</font>

1010
00:50:40,316 --> 00:50:41,316
<font color=#FFFF00>"Melirik"</font>

1011
00:50:41,316 --> 00:50:45,656
<font color=#FFFF00>Meski Su Hyeon sudah pergi, Shin Yul tetap senang dan bersiul.</font>

